<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>in the sun • under the sun</xh5><p> <i>in the sun—</i>exposed to light and warmth from the sun: People with paler skin may need just a few minutes <u>in the sun</u> at the beginning of the season.</p><p> <i>under the sun—</i>anywhere in the world: There’s no nation <u>under the sun</u> that doesn’t try to protect its military secrets.</p> </entry>
